data.description: Magnificent home in historic Brady Heights. Custom built 2001, vaulted ceilings & open spaces. 4 Bedrooms and 3 bathrooms. Double side Fireplace in Master bed/bath & enormous walk-in closet. Game room. Huge living areas. Must see this gorgeous home. Wonderful view of and within walking distance to downtown, BOK, OneOK Field, Guthrie Green. Great opportunity, needs cosmetic repairs (flooring, fresh paint) Sold As Is.
